      "parameters": {
        "content": "## STEP 1 - GET API KEY (YOURAPIKEY)\nCreate an account [here](https://fal.ai/) and obtain API KEY.\nIn the node \"Create Image\" set \"Header Auth\" and set:\n- Name: \"Authorization\"\n- Value: \"Key YOURAPIKEY\"",
